snippet.title: A Soldier's Reaction. #Holiday #shorts
snippet.description:
A military officer attempts to hunt down a terrorist, destroy a terrorist gang and deactivate the sleeper cells under his command.
Cast - Akshay Kumar, Sonakshi Sinha, Freddy Daruwala 
Directed by - A.R. Murugadoss


"Holiday: A Soldier Is Never Off Duty" is a high-octane action film which showcases Akshay Kumar's skills as an action star. The movie boasts of thrilling and intense action sequences, a well-written screenplay, and good performances from the lead actors. The plot of the movie revolves around the life of a soldier on vacation who stumbles upon a terrorist plot and decides to put a stop to it. He has to work with a local police officer and other officials to track down the terrorists and prevent them from carrying out their plan. The film also deals with themes of patriotism and selfless service to the nation. Overall, "Holiday: A Soldier Is Never Off Duty" is a well-crafted action thriller that is sure to keep audiences on the edge of their seats.

#HerneKatha #Ghanaghasya

Half a century ago, Taranath Sharma walked from Jhulaghat, Baitadi to Dadeldhura. His account of this difficult journey, "Ghanaghasya ko Ukalo Katda" was also included in the older Nepali textbook. 

Now, 55 years later, we decided to take the same journey up the steep hills of Ghanaghasya.

==== Why Herne Katha? ====
People behind Herne Katha spent 15 years of their lives doing journalism. One day they realised the need to tell more beautiful and inspiring stories of people, the real people. 

üëÄüëÄüëÄ Herne Katha üëÄüëÄüëÄ
Herne Katha is a web series produced by Tana Bana Digital in Nepal. We tell stories of people in the format of short documentaries. New episode of Herne Katha is published on  every  alternate Tuesdays (15 days) on YouTube. You can also watch Herne  Katha on Kantipur  Television every Tuesday 6:30 PM.

snippet.description:
Acv presents the second season of ‚ÄúSASTA BIIG BOSSS‚Äù
Chalo pehle brand waalo ka description daalte because PAISAAAA 

WOW Skin Science: ACV Shampoo & Face Wash

Amazon: https://amzn.to/3Xs8zo1 
Flipkart: https://bit.ly/3K06s7I
Nykaa: http://bit.ly/3HVUQ2W

BuyWow: http://bit.ly/3XnDn9y
(Use ASHISHWOW20 for an extra 20% discount)

Haan haan maalum
Hai hume bahut late ho gaya aane mein
Pure 10 nahi nahi 11 mahine lag gaye hume
Lekin tum log ko kya batau aisi fatti padi thi hum log ka kuch aisa project tha jisse plan karte karte karte 6-7 mahine aise nikle hume pata hi nai chala
Fir humne ye saal ka bigg boss dekha aur decide kiya abhi toh hum season 2 banaenge hi kaise bhi
Wo jo project hai jiski baat kar raha hu abhi back burner pe hai but promise hai hum usse kaise bhi aapke saamne laaengeüòç

Abhi subah ke 6 baje main ye description bathroom mein likh raha hu seth log toh please deri ke lie maaf kar do baaki tum log hi seth ho mere dhani ho muje maalum hai naraazgi hogi lekin utna hi pyaar bhi karte ho
Chalo abhi video ka Favourite part comment karo aur apna fav dialogue bhi likh lo

Chalo abhi production ka batao is video ka

Actors : wahi sasti team jisme dusre actors ki kami hoti, Akash Dodeja aka jadoo aka gareeb Kunal Chhabhria aka is baar wo kisi ke baap nahi gaya Vibhu Varshney humare video ke super star Simran Dhanwani rotlu pitbul Rohit Sadhwani belt waala anti-singham Tanish Sirwani sandaswala Grishim Nawani dubai waala Akash Jagtap thapad khaane waala Paras rupani playground ka rejected player, Ritesh Sadhwani bhi tha video mein bas ek scene mein kyunki saala gumm ho gaya tha Shivkumar Parthasarathy as humare big-bull Vivek Menon humare super super star as humare host
And ajay bhai jinhone teddy bear ka body double play kiya 

Writer & Director : main hi hu saalo
Editor : wo bhi main hi hu saalo
Background music - Vivek-Abhishek (inka channel dekho bahut talented hai mere bhai log : https://youtube.com/c/VIVEKABHISHEK)
Production Head: Jashan Sirwani & Tanish Sirwani (saara paisa ye log khaa jaate rent aur camera kaüò°)
DOP : Ujjawal Gayakwad,Sidharth Kedare
Assistant DOP : Hemendra Singh, Yogi

Sound : Satya Narayan

snippet.description:

1. KWACHA NEWARI RESTAURANT
ADDRESS: Chyasal, Belachhen road, Lalitpur, Nepal
üá≥üáµBARA (LENTIL PANCAKE): Add mustard oil in a hot pan, then add pancake batter (mixture of flour and water). Add green onions, carrots, cumin powder, tomato, garlic cloves, and eggs. Cook on each side for 2 minutes.
üá≥üáµCHATAMARI (NEPALI PIZZA): Add mustard oil in a hot pan, then add pancake batter (mixture of flour and water). Flatten batter with spoon, then add carrots, cucumbers, garlic cloves, tomato, coriander leaves, peas, and an egg.  Add salt, pepper, sesame and cumin powder.
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -  
2. KUMARI TEMPLE
ADDRESS: Lalitpur 09 Chyasal, Tin Mukhi Ganesh (Old Patan)
INTERVIEWEES: Niraj Ratna Bajracharya + Mohini Bajracharya
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -  
3. CHYASAL COMMUNITY SQUARE
ADDRESS:
üá≥üáµKACHILA (MARINATED RAW MINCED MEAT): Mince buffalo meat, then season with salt, garlic, cumin seeds and red chili powder. Pound the mixture, then add fenugreek seeds. Add turmeric powder to hot oil, then pour onto the meat and mix well. Top with green onions.
üá≥üáµNHYAPU (FRIED BUFFALO BRAIN): Boil innards & brain, then add mustard oil and turmeric powder. Fry until golden brown.
üá≥üáµHE (FRIED BUFFALO BLOOD CLOT): Add buffalo blood to the pan. Stir until the blood clots.
üá≥üáµSAPU MHICHA (BUFFALO TRIPE W/ BONE MARROW STUFFING): Take a piece of bone marrow and sew it in the tripe. Boil for 10-15 minutes. Drain the water, then fry. Add salt and cumin powder.
üá≥üáµCHOILA (SPICY GRILLED BUFFALO MEAT): Grill buffalo meat on a woodfire, then chop meat into smaller pieces and add turmeric powder & chili powder.
üá≥üáµME (FRIED BUFFALO TONGUE): Boil tongue. Add mustard oil to a pan, turmeric powder, and tongue meat.
üá≥üáµPUKALA (FRIED BUFFALO INNARDS): Boil innards. Add mustard oil to a pan, turmeric powder, and innards.
